          "description": "Diaphragmatic Expansion Contrast: Standing tall. Phase 1: Exhale fully, raise arms overhead. Phase 2: Inhale deeply, raise arms. Feel the difference. 5 reps each. Then Sphinx to Baby Cobra 5 reps.",
